---

Workflow (Detailed)

1. User submits query


2. Intent extractor generates CQL/search query


3. Orchestrator decides tool(s)


4. Search tool returns ~30 URLs


5. Ranking engine scores results


6. Top 3 URLs selected


7. Content extracted (+ linked pages if relevant)


8. LLM generates final response




